milestones.description: Shahzad has become the top scorer for AFG in ODIs with 2617 runs, going past Mohammad Nabi's 2565
This is the highest match aggregate (594) involving teams Scotland & Afghanistan in ODIs
Shahzad has scored 19 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Rahmat Shah's record
